{"tid":2385782,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★中原副主席：2021年 政治經濟環境明朗，購買力會爆發出來 樓價有較大升幅","createTime":"2021-01-29T08:13:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T12:55:51.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d6c58509080a59e47491445c9e53f0bf3c122c9a","tid":2385782,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:13:52.000Z","msg":"今年2021年，政治經濟環境較為明朗，潛在購買力將會爆發出來。進入今年1月，本港樓市有起動動作，多個地區的樓市成交明顯增加，而買家購買意欲亦積極，樓市小陽春提早出現。筆者預計今年樓價有比較大的升幅，幅度為7%。<br />\n<br />\n中原地產亞太區副主席兼住宅部總裁陳永傑<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210129/bkn-20210129111316282-0129_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20210129%2Fbkn-20210129111316282-0129_00842_001.html&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1ww9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=8ef88b84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210129/bkn-20210129111316282-0129_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2edae81de735e51adfa4318f45cd9229466f5c66","tid":2385782,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:14:22.000Z","msg":"政治經濟環境較為明朗<br />\n政治經濟環境較為明朗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46fd704f51eb5e97a05cda0114e001ea573abc7c","tid":2385782,"uid":51620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2edae81de735e51adfa4318f45cd9229466f5c66","tid":2385782,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:14:22.000Z","msg":"政治經濟環境較為明朗<br />\n政治經濟環境較為明朗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/n